# Authentification - Better Auth

Réf. Context7 : `/llmstxt/better-auth_llms_txt`, docs : better-auth.com/docs

## Configuration

```typescript
import { betterAuth } from "better-auth";
import { drizzleAdapter } from "better-auth/adapters/drizzle";
import { tanstackStartCookies } from "better-auth/tanstack-start";

export const auth = betterAuth({
  database: drizzleAdapter(db, { provider: "pg", schema }),
  trustedOrigins: [env.CORS_ORIGIN],
  emailAndPassword: { enabled: true },
  plugins: [tanstackStartCookies()],  // doit être en dernier dans le tableau
});
```

- Config : `packages/auth/src/index.ts`
- `tanstackStartCookies()` : gère les cookies pour signIn/signUp côté TanStack Start

## Routes API

- Handler auth : `apps/web/src/routes/api/auth/$.ts`
- `auth.handler(request)` pour GET et POST

## Middleware session

```typescript
// apps/web/src/middleware/auth.ts
const authMiddleware = createMiddleware().server(async ({ next, request }) => {
  const session = await auth.api.getSession({ headers: request.headers });
  return next({ context: { session } });
});
```

## Client côté navigateur

```typescript
import { createAuthClient } from "better-auth/react";
export const authClient = createAuthClient({});
```

- `authClient.useSession()` pour React
- `authClient.signIn.email()`, `authClient.signUp.email()`, `authClient.signOut()`
- Callbacks : `onSuccess`, `onError` dans les options

## Routes protégées

- `beforeLoad` : appeler `getUser()` (server function avec authMiddleware)
- `loader` : vérifier `context.session` et `redirect({ to: "/login" })` si absent

## Env requises

- `BETTER_AUTH_SECRET` (min 32 chars)
- `BETTER_AUTH_URL`
- `CORS_ORIGIN`
